Package: mupager
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Terminal document viewer with pixel-perfect rendering
 mupager renders PDFs, EPUB, and other documents with pixel-perfect
 fidelity using the Kitty graphics protocol. It includes Neovim
 integration for viewing documents inside your editor.
